    "body": "client.write is sync except if it needs to use zlib.deflate\r\n\r\nIt would be possible to either : \r\n* making it sync by using https://nodejs.org/api/zlib.html#zlib_zlib_deflatesync_buf_options\r\n* adding a callback to client.write so user don't assume that client.write is sync\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2015-05-19T12:31:46Z",
